<h1>Welcome to Budget App</h1>

<section class="home-content">
    <p>
        With this application you can manage your budget: 
        you have a list of transactions associated with a category, so that you can 
        see how much money you spent and on what.
    </p>

    <p>
        To use this application you need to sign up or log in.
    </p>
</section>

<div class="home-actions">
    <% if user_signed_in? %> 
        <%= link_to "My Categories", categories_path, class: "my-categories-link" %>
    <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "login-link" %>
        <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "sign-up-link" %>
    <% end %>
</div>
